{
  "stem": "17821.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 113.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he told the boss, we don't need any foreign experts here, we'll do it on our own.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was so unpleasant that it was decided that Martin wouldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we couldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But eventually he got this job at Vickers-Armstrong where we would have been able to stay.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But soon the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when things were going bad in France, the trains in the south of France had already been stopped, so there was no-- no trains going.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said to my boss, I think I'd better go to England with my daughter and join Martin there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the very next day, we had to come back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They would have liked to keep-- Vickers-Armstrong would have liked to keep him because he was very useful in manufacturing the-- it was called the Wellington or some kind of plane.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But so he was saved from actively being engaged in a plane that would have gone to kill people, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's a point-of-view too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So his company got in touch with the French Embassy in London-- what Martin was supposed to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed him, but he's a French citizen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they said he had to go back to France and join his company.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went back and he joined.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sent him back home because they hadn't decided what to do with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then about a week or so later then, they-- he received his consignment and he was to be a liaison with the British Army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- he went to the north of France and was with a group of colonels and captains of the British anti-aircraft.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
